 Syntax:  .set car

Results:  This command allows you to set whether linefeeds are sent after
          every line along with carriage returns. (\n\r instead of \n)
          Use this on VAX/VMS systems or whenever your text seems to step
          down diagnally.
                         like this line
                                       and this line does
          This command is a TOGGLE. Meaning, every time you type it, it
          will either turn the option on or off.

